About this item

  • X-Temp technology adapts to temperature, environment and activity to keep you cool and dry
  • Moisture wicking fabric
  • Tag-free neck label

    • About this item

    Important Made in USA Origin Disclaimer: For certain items sold by Walmart on Walmart.com, the displayed country of origin information may not be accurate or consistent with manufacturer information. For updated, accurate country of origin data, it is recommended that you rely on product packaging or manufacturer information.
    X-Temp technology adapts to temperature, environment and activity to keep you cool and dry for all day comfort. Blended 4.5 ounce ringspun fabric for the softest hand in performance tees. Moisture wicking fabric with dynamic vapor control.Tag-free neck label. Double-needle cover-seamed neck with three-quarter inch lay flat collar and shoulder to shoulder tape for durability.
    Hanes Big Men's X-temp Short Sleeve Tee:
    • Blended 4.5 ounce ringspun fabric
    • X-Temp technology adapts to temperature, environment and activity to keep you cool and dry
    • Moisture wicking fabric
    • Tag-free neck label
    • Double-needle cover-seamed neck with three-quarter inch lay flat collar
    • Shoulder to shoulder tape for durability
    • Crew neckline
    • Short sleeves
    • Machine wash cold

    Directions:

    Fabric Care Instructions: Care Instructions: Turn inside out. Machine wash cold. Remove promptly after wash. Dark colors separately. Only non-chlorinated bleach if needed. Tumble dry low. Cool iron if needed exlcusive of decoration. Do not dry clean or use fabric softener.
